OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778166668
OL,3,CFire crews tackling blaze at
OL,4,Cgymnastics centre
OL,6,FCrews from Aylesbury, Thame, Amersham,
OL,7,FBuckingham, High Wycombe, Slade Park
OL,8,Fand Leighton Buzzard as well as four
OL,9,Fofficers, are at the scene.
OL,11,FThey are using four sets of breathing
OL,12,Fapparatus and two hose reel jets.
OL,14,FRoad closures are in place while crews
OL,15,Fcontinue to work at the scene. Thames
OL,16,FValley Police are also there.
OL,18,FThis is a developing, more to follow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/2
